<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0038a" xml:id="I01.0014.0038a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 14</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>比丘郭曇勝造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陰</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0038a0101">
<lb ed="I" n="0038a02" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a03" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a04" type="honorific"/>但越主梁洪相
<lb ed="I" n="0038a05" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a06" type="honorific"/>　　梁歸喜
<lb ed="I" n="0038a07" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038a08" type="honorific"/></p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0038b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0038b0101">　　　　　　　　大代延昌四年歲次乙未四月一日
<lb ed="I" n="0038b02" type="honorific"/>比丘郭□勝　造石像一區。為忘弟子　曇豐。
<lb ed="I" n="0038b03" type="honorific"/>夫大覺淟□□積善。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0038b0301" n="0038b0301"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038b0301" n="0038b0301"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0038b0301"/>以成其功。四到輪迴。何能超其累。
<lb ed="I" n="0038b04" type="honorific"/>是以□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">晉</unclear>脩諸利。功益當時。自靈波沖寂。神光遷<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">苑</unclear>。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0038001" n="0038001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0038001" n="0038001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038001" n="0038001"/>雖<anchor xml:id="end0038001"/>復
<lb ed="I" n="0038b05" type="honorific"/>漸影園□。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">光</unclear>潛□□。自非識體玄宗。栖心妙竟。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">沖</unclear>慮建于靈祇。
<lb ed="I" n="0038b06" type="honorific"/>像法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">開</unclear>□□。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">願</unclear>使忘者神生天堂。縱志八定。彌勒一其。值生不退。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">現</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0038b07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">世</unclear>伏災。四大休□。功□寵祿。子孫樊熾。門族雍和。非□永絕三途曠火輪催軸
<lb ed="I" n="0038b08" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　三有四生。悟<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0038b0801" n="0038b0801"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038b0801" n="0038b0801"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0038b0801"/>生忍。庶□尠　　<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">散</unclear>。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0038002" n="0038002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0038002" n="0038002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038002" n="0038002"/>冀<anchor xml:id="end0038002"/>隆剋就。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陽</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0038c0101">忘父郭僧景
<lb ed="I" n="0038c02" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c03" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c04" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c05" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c06" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c07" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0038c08" type="honorific"/>　梁丰一心</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0038d01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0038d0101">比丘道和從兄郭□保
<lb ed="I" n="0038d02" type="honorific"/>比丘曇歆從姪柏尉
<lb ed="I" n="0038d03" type="honorific"/>比丘曇喜從姪雙伯
<lb ed="I" n="0038d04" type="honorific"/>比丘曇妙息郭達
<lb ed="I" n="0038d05" type="honorific"/>比丘曇興息郭顯
<lb ed="I" n="0038d06" type="honorific"/>比丘道<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0038003" n="0038003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0038003" n="0038003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0038003" n="0038003"/>藻<anchor xml:id="end0038003"/>外生阿勝
<lb ed="I" n="0038d07" type="honorific"/>比丘曇智姊郭安□
<lb ed="I" n="0038d08" type="honorific"/>亡竇叔□□郭<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">真</unclear>安妻□</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
