</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0039b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0039b0101">梁光祖思集相母李　安容女
<lb ed="I" n="0039b02" type="honorific"/>梁足仁保織閻陵姜女阿□
<lb ed="I" n="0039b03" type="honorific"/>梁石祖□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">哉</unclear>鄧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">拯</unclear>生女□非
<lb ed="I" n="0039b04" type="honorific"/>梁洪興天覆馬春好女僧姬
<lb ed="I" n="0039b05" type="honorific"/>梁迴　騃洛楊供妃女軍<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0039001" n="0039001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0039001" n="0039001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0039001" n="0039001"/>老<anchor xml:id="end0039001"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0039b06" type="honorific"/>梁洪祖難當柳栢醜女眉容
<lb ed="I" n="0039b07" type="honorific"/>梁承祖思儀衛雙眉女迎男
<lb ed="I" n="0039b08" type="honorific"/>梁天□歸洛女醜多女敬愛
<lb ed="I" n="0039b09" type="honorific"/>梁□□□□□□好女雷當
<lb ed="I" n="0039b10" type="honorific"/>□□□□妙容姿</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
