<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0039c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0039c0101">　比丘法□
<lb ed="I" n="0039c02" type="honorific"/>比丘郭曇勝供養
<lb ed="I" n="0039c03" type="honorific"/>傅珍國一心供養
<lb ed="I" n="0039c04" type="honorific"/>崔亮一心
